/**
 * Z-Wave Switch All On of All Off
 * When user toggles this switch a All On or All Off message will be sent to ALL
 * Z-Wave nodes that support the Switch All Command Class
 *
 * The node ID used in the zwave binding MUST be the ID of any one node that
 * supports the SwithAll command class.
 * Usually devices such as dimmers or regular wall switches will support the
 * Z-Wave Switch All command class
 */
Switch AllOnOff "All On/Off" {zwave="1:command=SWITCH_ALL"}